 diving team.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9967124081523173, \"rank\": 0.0032984214906183512, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"another Olympics\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"his former bosses\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"a vacancy\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10metre synchro platform diving team\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was effectively told he could come back into the fold if Noah Williams and Matty Lee failed to win a medal at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fold\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They came up short and it opened the door for the 30-year-o